abstract: >
  AI-readable appendix addendum for SΔϕ-66. It uses enterprise agentic AI cost
  reporting as an illustrative case for Delegation Completion Cost, separating
  AI capability from low-cost AI delegation after delegation, retrieval,
  verification, repair, and application costs are included.
